    <text id="F0111T">
        <front id="d2">
            <div1 type="summary" id="d3">
                <p>Crum writes to her lover about the latest stories from home.</p>
            </div1>
        </front>
        <body id="d4">
            <div1 type="letter" id="d5">
                <head>
                    <name type="recipient">her lover</name>
                </head>

                <opener>
                    <dateline>
                        <date value="1865-02-03">Februray 3, 1865</date>
                        <name type="place">Franklin County, PA</name>
                    </dateline>
                    <salute>Dear Lover</salute>
                </opener>

                <p>It is with greatest pleasure that I seat myself this morning to pen you a few
                        <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> to let you <orig reg="know">no</orig> that I am in
                    tolerable good health at this time and <orig reg="hoping">hopeing</orig> these
                    few imperfect lines May find you in Considerable good health I received your
                    Dear kind letter the 23 inst on the 30 of last Month it was A long time of
                    coming to me you had stated in your letter that my letter <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> coming to you i <orig reg="wrote">rote</orig> it on the <del
                        hand="h1"/> and took it to the office on the 12 i then they left it lay it
                    while before they Mailed it but i told <unclear>hoopes</unclear> they <orig
                        reg="shouldn't">shoulden not</orig>
                    <orig reg="leave">leve</orig> the letter lay so long before they them Mail
                        them.<pb n="2"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> Tell you that <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> and Emanda had <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> here two weeks <orig reg="ago"
                        >A go</orig> and Elijah <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> that you had your arm <del
                        hand="h1"/> severely by rowling <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> forts but wether it <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> i do not no i could
                    hardely believe it or else you would have told me A bout it i was sorry when i
                    herd it i Dont no where else she herd it she would not tell me she told me that
                    the girls tells her evry thing about you i must now change my <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    or <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> you will get tired reading such stuff now i Must <del
                        hand="h1"/> you A sketch A bout the wether here now we have had very cold
                    wether for the last two weeks it was Cold enough to frese the horns of A muley
                        <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> we have had the best sleighing<pb n="3"/>the last week that
                    we have had for some years i never saw <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> sleighs going as i did
                    ther has <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> they war just runing Day and <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> i must tell you
                    that the <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> to make A nother Draft on <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> of the Month you May
                    be glad <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>you Aint in it fer it will take verry near all the boys
                    in our towns <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> i was sorry when i herd that you was expecting a
                    battle there with the rebs i just wish the rebs would <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> up so the
                    war would be over before the <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> up until they <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> bload up i do wish the war was ended and you was at home and
                    then we would have the fun of going to Millerstown i would like to go out there
                    to see how times is out there i suppose you would like to go too<pb n="4"/>to
                    have some fun i hope <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> have some fun two i would rite <del
                        hand="h1"/> to you but i am sush A poor <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> to rite letters i
                    Dont want you <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> to any person for <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> wether the people <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> rite i Dont care wether <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> rite so well but still i can love you with all my heart and
                    soul well i think i must Bring my few remarks to A close some more at present
                    but still remain your affectionate friend <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> wont forget you as
                    long as i live <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> at present <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> if you please <del rend="none" hand="h1"/>
                    <del rend="none" hand="h1"/> comes to hand</p>

                <closer>
                    <salute>None</salute>
                    <signed>Catherine A. Crum </signed>
                    <seg type="postscript">
                        <name type="recipient"> Eli H Crum </name>
                    </seg>
                </closer>
            </div1>
        </body>
    </text>
